This paper deals with 3D object recognition using multiple data representations and introduces new Volumetric CNN architectures. This work involves computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML) techniques, which are covered under cs.CV and cs.LG. The paper also discusses the use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and their architectures, which are relevant to cs.AI. Additionally, the paper deals with robotics systems, which falls under cs.RO. Finally, the paper involves the use of 3D object recognition, which can be categorized under cs.GR.
